title: We Deliver a Great Living Experience...Courtland Place Apartments !!!

posting_body: ['See this Unique "Top-floor" Apartment Home now ready for an August 15th or September 1st move-in.', 'Choose a Peaceful South facing apartment with Stunning views all for only $965.00.', 'Our apartment homes feature Warm, Inviting and Spacious Layouts, Magnificent Closet Space, Full Kitchens with Great Counter Space.', 'Come visit this Beautiful Contemporary building and move into your New Neighborhood this Summer.', 'The Courtland Apartments is a 55+ Community offering nicely updated flats with all new carpets, hardwood floors in the kitchen and bathroom and updated or all new appliances.', 'We can also provide additional on-site storage with ample street parking.', 'Please feel free to bring your furry friends along when moving to our "Pet Friendly" building, accepting both Kitties and Doggies.', 'Income restriction apply.', 'NAMED FOR THE MOUNTAIN that looms large over the South End when the clouds part, Rainier Valley is one of the most ethnically and economically diverse areas in the Northwest.', 'Most popular is Columbia City, a hamlet of hip along Rainier Avenue that boasts many magnificent restaurants, access to great shopping, local eateries and bus stops just steps from your front door.', 'Stop by for a tour and check out the many abundant options in this diverse neighborhood, which is on the National Register of Historic Places to live.', 'Please remember, applications are taken on a first come, first served basis.', 'Call our Friendly Leasing Team today and let us be your housing provider extraordinaire while putting your house hunting days behind you !!!', 'Courtland Place Apartments', '3621 33rd Ave South', 'Seattle, Washington 98144', 'show contact info', '** Offering 12 month leases terms', '** Sign on the dotted line by completing your application on-line: $45.00', '** Pictures presented are similar to the current apartment offered for lease - #706', '** Lock down your new apartment by presenting holding deposit of $400.00 through 8/31/22']
